{"tid":564570,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[J2] 年初三晚 11:05 《網戰》","createTime":"2018-02-18T06:47:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T09:22:15.000Z","uid":77192,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fa335f259bf8f149c21869eb1c01e617e8fc82bd","tid":564570,"uid":77192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:47:55.000Z","msg":"唔知大家對2016年網絡挑機仲有冇印象，我地開片OPEN VIDEO參與左節目最後一集 ，節目播出後， TVB 同我地講想改革引入新既製作，話想做乜就做啦。<br />\n咁我哋就做咗一集一個鐘頭嘅電視劇，呢套TVB電視劇都算喺有今生冇來世，男女主角張建聲同吳凱昕都唔屬於TVB。本來以為TVB同蕭生個仔打官司，會浪費晒所有台前幕後嘅工作人員嘅心血，電視劇無限期雪藏。<br />\n點知年廿九導演開電視睇到有節目預告，雖不能夠稱得上是好作品，但都希望大家可以年初三支持下呢部作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果大家對作品或者TVB有咩問題，答到盡答 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/18/144558_2c9742a6ef3ba0baa27cd8a6bb0b8501.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2F144558_2c9742a6ef3ba0baa27cd8a6bb0b8501.JPG&h=56a12492&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C27_5xNKTUY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC27_5xNKTUY&d=0%2FjgaY9T%2BBAXZAwhpOOyogCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=57a691f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C27_5xNKTUY</a>"},{"pid":"e94cb3c545209e5ca0c080f56ce34e09a3ce7688","tid":564570,"uid":45545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T09:10:19.000Z","msg":"正評比你嘅 有冇得上網重溫<br />\n<br />\nBtw加油"},{"pid":"9b803299d13badaa535d3f08ab966a7438bddb9a","tid":564570,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T09:47:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://programme.tvb.com/drama/thewarnet/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprogramme.tvb.com%2Fdrama%2Fthewarnet%2F&d=0%2FjgaY9T%2BBAXZAwhpOOyogCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=885e06e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://programme.tvb.com/drama/thewarnet/</a><br />\n大台網居然可以完全冇招積